title: New Zealand DEM Hillshade - Igor
description: Hillshade generated from the New Zealand LiDAR 1m DEM and New Zealand Contour-Derived 8m DEM (where no 1m DEM data exists) using the -igor option in GDAL. This renders a softer hillshade that tries to minimize effects on other map features.
